This directory contains bash scripts for various tasks including configuration of the OS and starting/stopping ROS2 nodes.

Tools in the top level directory are compatible and applicable to all nodes. Node specific tools are in folders per device as below.


	motor:

		Tools for the RPi 3 that controlls the Sabertooth motor drive and 24v relays.

		start.sh
		-	Starts ROS2 nodes

		stop.sh	
		-	Stops ROS2 nodes


	ai:

		Tools for the RPi 4 that controls the RPLidar and Camera


	ws:

		Tools
